et我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地心諗同我做朋友都影衰佢<br />\n叫我温書去exchange咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友都唔係只係戰友<br />\n只係異性對我好<br />\n我先ff"},{"pid":"5bf52a0db94d0f3cf969235955b5099a8a6e1523","tid":44690,"uid":49984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好意思<br />\n我寧願人地唔對我好<br />\n搞到無心機温書<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又等炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會溫書麻醉自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無精神温<br />\n聽日又等炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無聊2科佢教我但都炒<br />\n因為掛住諗佢<br />\n但佢唔會知<br />\n只係我諗多<br />\n大家睇完whatsapp對話都覺得好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無異性朋友係易諗多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下引佢講啲無聊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />約下佢</blockquote><br />\n無啦<br />\n無聊嘢已經唔應<br />\n以前會陪我吹"},{"pid":"c718f8a59ff7831d07d47a705f240fb657e283f7","tid":44690,"uid":49984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩返佢轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好難架。唔係player格。玩人會玩返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有能力咪傻啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經比人已讀不回 明明提醒左自己唔好沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望過一排就淡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反正都起碼開sem先見到"},{"pid":"14fe53b76b71460765c9c451fc2ace31da5c18f6","tid":44690,"uid":48366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:25:59.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"f0c5e470909