img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次俾人已讀不回隔一排就撩佢講野<br />\n但無啦我地之間已經無野再連繫無任何關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有事揾佢<br />\n無事聊人好奇怪<br />\n但有事先揾佢<br />\n人地又覺得我只係利用佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無啦 <br />\n照下鏡就知人地點睇我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同學關係？<br />\n係嘅應該可以r到野講</blockquote><br />\n佢考完試<br />\n等開sem啦<br />\n其實一開始無鍾意<br />\n但對我好<br />\n我就會亂諗嘢<br />\n唔再揾我<br />\n我好唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慣咗佢突然彈一句<br />\n佢温書既狀況黎<br />\n但考完之前佢都無揾我<br />\n我考完佢都唔會揾我<br />\n可能下次講嘢係reg科<br />\n但嗰陣無睇清楚<br />\nreg科嗰日去咗旅行"},{"pid":"f6a0cee725d12e7a772abf4872305cf2e8c4221a","tid":44690,"uid":49984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"即係最可以拉近距離既日子都失去唏"},{"pid":"d0dae59fc7f485220f6ccbadb4462084bba8e759","tid":44690,"uid":49984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:38:10.000Z","msg":"過份在意但人地唔會覺得一回事<br />\n加上衰咗都會對住 <br />\n再識人都係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709df1cdb52cafa34da14e61763eb60c2a06bf14","tid":44690,"uid":49984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相都無<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a3ba5fc932014ca970e9912c8f17986b03301d","tid":44690,"uid":24490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"冇動力去做任何野 只係不停咁等待奇蹟出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0929c7180939b437560b587f5a51fc10d7ac5d65","tid":44690,"uid":34979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:17:07.0